description: Retrieves the behavior configuration of Route 53 Resolver behavior for a single VPC from Amazon Virtual Private Cloud.

parameters.name: ResourceId
parameters.description: Resource ID of the Amazon VPC that you want to get information about.

nested_items.name: ResolverConfig
nested_items.description: Information about the behavior configuration of Route 53 Resolver behavior for the VPC you specified in the GetResolverConfig request.

nested_items.name: ResourceId
nested_items.description: The ID of the Amazon Virtual Private Cloud VPC or a Route 53 Profile that you're configuring Resolver for.

nested_items.name: OwnerId
nested_items.description: The owner account ID of the Amazon Virtual Private Cloud VPC.

nested_items.name: AutodefinedReverse
